{"about_the_game":"In Volatility, explore an interconnected world unfolding as you acquire new abilities, each region brimming with secrets to uncover!<br />\r\nLeft to die in a collapsing artificial world, you must learn how to escape it with the help of its few inhabitants still sane.<br />\r\nWhy is this world being engulfed by its own core? What happened to the people who lived here? Who are you and how did you end up here? <br />\r\n<br />\r\nInspired by both modern metroidvanias and adventure games of the '90s and early 2000s, the game sees you conquering a world of dungeons and treasure.<br />\r\nEvery newly acquired ability means new ways to interact with your environments like slashing chains, shooting far-away objects and riding on laser beams!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- An adventure spanning several floating islands and their dungeon interiors.<br />\r\n- Earn and upgrade Gems to broaden your combat and puzzle-solving options.<br />\r\n- Engage in widely varied gameplay including third-person shooting, top-down action, and on-rails shooting.<br />\r\n- Collect secret treasures to power up and learn more about the world.<br />\r\n- Help survivors stay alive and sane in their broken world.<br />\r\n- Escape the collapsing pocket dimension before it's too late!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304290/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735915497","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304290/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1735915497","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304290/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735915497","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304290/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735915497","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descripto